        "subject": "LU-9211 tests: fix ost-pool non-zero exit status",
        "message": "LU-9211 tests: fix ost-pool non-zero exit status\n\nTests ost-pools/7[abc] passed but return exit code != 0.\nost_pools_init and cleanup_pools called at the start and\nend of the ost-pool test case execution, when do_facet\ncalled to list non-existing pool, it returns with exit\nstatus 2.\n\nAs this is not test specific error, fix to redirect this\nerror to /dev/null and return status 0.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jadhav Vikram <jadhav.vikram@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: I9a1d1636dcafc2ee88184fef419e421d55ab71b8\n"
